name: WebNet Hosting
description: Managed Dedicated Servers and Cloud Host
overview:
Celebrating our 10th year in business in 2012, WebNet Hosting is an industry leading provider of Shared, Reseller, VPS, Dedicated, eCommerce web hosting. Privately held and based in Rockville Maryland, the company was founded in 2003 by Founder & current Chairman PJ Taei, who started the company from his parents home in Gaithersburg, Maryland. Since then, WebNet Hosting has grown from a small hosting company to a profitable world leading industry recognized hosting provider with more than 10,000 customers.

WebNet Hosting has distinguished itself as a leader in the Web Hosting community by providing true customer satisfaction with the ability to provide 24/7 non stop service and optimum uptime since 2003. We are a friendly accessible group of experts which strive in providing our customers with pleasant web experience and honoring support.

WebNet Hosting remains as focused as ever on providing our customers with an excellent hosting experience. We are confident our array of value-added services, free tools, scripts, open source solutions, and high speed hosting servers will lead your business forward.
